text: Oliver Grüner (born 12 March 1966) is a German rower. He competed in the men's quadruple sculls event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:German male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of West Germany Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Frankfurt
